  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to a high heat, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then boil a kettle</p><p>Combine <strong>half</strong> your <strong>curry powder </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>in a bowl with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>and mix it all together<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>tandoori marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
