    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the onion has softened</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
