        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>marinated chicken</strong> to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Put the tray under the grill for 10-12 min or until the chicken is starting to char and is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>tandoori chicken</strong></p>",
