      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> tandoori chicken</strong> over the <strong>curried giant couscous</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> ginger & garlic yoghurt</strong> all over and garnish with the<strong> chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
